name: Fill Wooden Block: Wood Puzzle
description:
Fill Wooden Block is a addictive puzzle block game. The gameplay is easy, drag the different blocks into place to match the puzzle. if you like puzzle game, Fill Wooden Block is your best choose.
HOW TO PLAY
1: Drag blocks to fill up the frame.
2: Blocks cannot be rotated.
3: No time limit!
Play with Wooden Blocks’ Community and share your interest to your family, friends.
